➜行业首创“终身双免”，预售6.99万元起，长安欧尚X5真会玩儿
http://www.sohu.com/a/425973886_99994080	18434
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201020/2c0d6038ec4c42c28f13021026d2efbd.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
